Girls (10.00), the less than excellent comedy Absolutely (10.30) and the
uninspired Sticky Moments On Tour With Julian Cary (1.30).
Evening's best bet, if last week's programme is any guide, will be BBC2's
States Of Mind (8.10) which shows how a small lumberjacking community in
Oregon reacts to a remote government decision to declare the northern
spotted owl an endangered species.
